text:
51 year old Janet Jackson has come out to deny claims that she is now dating ex-boyfriend 45 year old Germain Dupri. The two have been linked together ever since Janet Jackson’s divorce to Qatari Billionaire Wissam Al Mana.

Sources say that Janet and Dupri are just friends and there is absolutely no romance brewing between the two.

It is alleged that after Janet and Germain broke up, they had a period in which they lost touch. They later overcame that and found friendship again. It is alleged that Janet Jackson and Germain Dupri trust each other and they have been talking more after Janet’s divorce.

Sources told American entertainment website ENews that Janet Jackson is not in a position to get involved with someone else at this time.

“Janet is really not in a position to get involved with someone at this time,” our source explained. “She is open though for something more down the line. They are in the talks of working on some new projects.”

The singer continues with her State Of The World tour across USA while remaining devote dto being a simgle mum to her son Eissa Al Mana.

Source: EOnline
title: Janet Jackson not in a position to date again
